            <div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Hard bounces are permanent failures — invalid addresses or non-existent domains — and must be removed on the first bounce. Soft bounces are temporary (full mailbox, server downtime) and warrant 2-3 retries before removal.</p></div></div>
